case_id: shaft-keyway
possible: true
awkwardness: medium
pain_points[2]:
  - "Slot alignment to cylinder is offset-based instead of axis/face constrained."
  - "No dedicated keyway helper, so dimensions are manually coordinated."
proposed_features[2]:
  - "Axis-aligned slot primitive for shafts."
  - "Reference constraints against cylindrical faces/axes."
reviewer_verdict: "Possible with existing primitives, but alignment readability is weaker than desired."
